column5: Happy Birthday mon chum!!! Have yourself a super day
happy b day Paul....... Leechman has the present I sent you so go on over and collect.   Art
Happy Birthday Buddy! Get ur   out there and catch a big bass before your luck runs out  (**joking**)  Have a good one, MTBF
Yahoo Paul. Hope yer having a great day.
Hey Jacques.....quit being soooooo lazy and go walk across your front lawn and knock on Paul's door to wish him a B'day in person!!!!!!

Art... I received the present and think I'll keep it cause it's too nice      May be I'll be nice and give it to him when he get's back   Hey Steve.... I tried but he's gone fishing    :lol:   I'll try at sundown...
Happy Birthday, hope you have a super day.  Joey
the older he gets the grumpier he gets!
HA!!!... now he's older than me!!!  Go poach over your limit of "Green Trout"... I won't tell!!!  Best Fishes to Paul on his B'day!!!
Happy BDay Paul,  may your next year be full of new bird species to take pictures of.  I was going to wish for you to catch nice fish but you already have that under control.
Thanks All.....   Dan ..   You should see the pics of the green heron i saw fishing at McBay lastnight .....and the size of the perch he caught
Yes I should see the pics   but I don't!!!
